52/58 fire pets ALSo have spell changes:
<br />

<br />
58 fire cast:
<br />
Arch shielding, Diamondskin, O'Kiels FLickering flame on self.
<br />

<br />
For offence it cast Smolder, Enticemenet of flame, Ice Shock, Conflagration, also a "Force struck effect" so I dont know what that is.
<br />

<br />

<br />
52 pet cast:
<br />
Greater SHielding, Steelskin, O'Kiels Flickering FLame, Fire elemental Aura on self
<br />

<br />
For offence: Garrisons Mighty Mana Shock, Bonds of Force, Elnericks Entombment of Ice, Ice Shock
<br />

<br />

