<br />
First off, this is pretty damn cool. If things had been like this when I rolled up my wizard, I donno if I WOULDA rolled up my wizard, haha. Who needs Ice Comet if I can be a mage and get a pet that does it for me??
<br />

<br />
But, I saw this list of spells and the previous, and thought I'd throw some input on what seems to be going on. From the list of spells I saw for Child of Ro, it seems to have 52 and lower wizard spells. This would give it IC (49), Rend (49), Manaskin (52), Pillar of Frost (51), Tishan's Discord (51), Lure of Frost (52), Draught of Fire (51) etc. Arch Shielding is 44, and so is np
<br />

<br />
For the lvl 58 pet's spell list (going from what I quoted), the pet is rockin lvl 44 and lower wizzy spells. Smolder is not a wizard spell, so not sure what you mean.... maybe Conflagration which is 44. Enticement of flame is 44 (and completely sucks for mana/dmg ratio... gimp lure-resists wise tho), Ice Shock is 34(?), Diamondskin is 44 (and is a damn nice damage absord shield for 400+... I don't use it myself even, it normally requires dots), and the force struck message you are seeing is conflag's lvl 44 sister nuke Force Strike (spell interrupter).
<br />

<br />
The 52 pet seems to have an odd assortment of spells. The entombment of ice (a nuke with 24 second root component) is a 39 spell, but everything else is 34 or lower.  Steelskin (34), ice shock (34), Garrisons mighty mana Shock (20!), Bonds of Force (low lvl cousin to Atol's, this one a 29). Unless it was missed, the lvl 39 nuke, Lightning Shock, is not present, and that is too bad. Does a nice punch for 400+.
<br />

<br />
So, my question is now: What is the level of the pets? Is the 52 spell pet lvl 39-44? The 58 pet 44-48? The 62(child of ro, not sure on level) 52?
<br />

<br />
Inquiring minds want to know.
<br />

<br />
And grats to all magi if this goes live. I just dinged 52 last night, kinda funny to think that every 62+ mage with his fire pet spell will basically have a somewhat dumb me in his pocket.<br />_________________<br />Infirno
